Habitats

Fisheries

We are measuring catch within your EEZ.

We need catch for at least 10 years (20 is better).

Ideally, we would also have status (at least B/BMSY, bonus is F/FMSY).

What we can do in this workshop: - remove species - improve meancatch estimates

(no matter what were not calcluting b_bmsy) But what we could do is improve the parrot fishes every year

Look at the list. Do you have it? Is the catch represented in EEZ ie fished in the EEZ? Update data for those species, recalculate either with only those species, or mix-and-match SAUP and local data. Cannot add new species to meancatch because need b_bmsy estimates! Or we

We will discuss whether the data you have is representative of that.

Get a list of species, years, and whether its caught within EE
